Package: ai.vital.vitalsigns.model

[Java] Class ClassPropertiesHelper

      • ai.vital.vitalsigns.model.ClassPropertiesHelper

      • Base class to access class properties. There should be a single helper class for each generated graph object class. GraphObject.properties() 'dynamic' static method returns an instance of this helper. Subclasses containsDynamically generated helper class
